Subject: Wrestling
data: 1 The sportsperson Geeta Phogat is associated with which of the following games? A Archery B Weightlifting C Boxing D Wrestling Answer: Option [D]

2 Internatinal Olympic Committee(IOC) has dropped which of the following games from the 2020 games? The IOC acted after reviewing the 26 sports in the current Olympic format and the ousted game will now be listed with seven others in applying for inclusion in 2020. A Badminton B Baseball C Wresting D Squash Answer: Option [C]
3 Which of the following players won Silver Medal in London Olympics in 2012? A Yogeshwar Dutt B Sushil Kumar C Geetika Jakhar D Ravinder Singh Answer: Option [B]
4 Which two players won Bronze Medal in London Olympics? A Vinesh and Geetika Jakhar B Mausam Khatri and Alka Tomar C Yogeshwar Dutt and Sushil Kumar D None of these Answer: Option [C]
5 Which Indian Wrestler won the Gold Medal in Incheon Asian games? A Yogeshwar Dutt B Narsingh Pancham Yadav C Geetika Jakhar D Bajrang Answer: Option [A]
